data.description: This beautiful corner lot has 2 BR/2 BA plus a den and a 2-car garage.   High ceilings, split floor plan, dining room, eat-in kitchen, walk-in closets, hurricane protection, tons of light and on a quiet, private lot. Close to shopping, restaurants, and houses of worship. Vizcaya is an active 55+ gated community with resort style pool, Har-Tru tennis courts, pickle ball, bocce courts, fitness room, card rooms and many more activities. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home. Can be rented immediately!
